{"title":"Trailander Trail Groomer maintains MTB trails for snowy fat biking heaven","link":"https://bikerumor.com/2021/02/23/trailander-trail-groomer-maintains-mtb-trails-for-snowy-fat-biking-heaven/","date":1614099018000,"content":"<div id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"><div><p>Finnish company Trailander have developed a mountain bike trail groomer for maintaining trails in snowy conditions. Pulled along by a snow mobile, this steel frame contraption smooths over the surface of the snow, reinstating the route of snow-buried trails, or creating entirely new ones. If you’re an avid fat biker, you may want to petition your local trail association to invest in one of these bad boys…</p><h2>Trailander Trail Groomer for snowy MTB trails</h2><p><a href=\"https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/trailander-bike-route-plane-track-clearer-trail-groomer.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/trailander-bike-route-plane-track-clearer-trail-groomer.jpg?ezimgfmt=rs:484x363/rscb8/ng:webp/ngcb8\" alt=\"trailander bike route plane trail groomer\" width=\"1200\" height=\"900\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb8 src ng ngcb8 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/trailander-bike-route-plane-track-clearer-trail-groomer.jpg?ezimgfmt=rs:484x363/rscb8/ng:webp/ngcb8\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/trailander-bike-route-plane-track-clearer-trail-groomer.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb8 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/trailander-bike-route-plane-track-clearer-trail-groomer-297x223.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb8 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/trailander-bike-route-pla